

{"id":5383,"date":"2023-08-23T17:07:42","date_gmt":"2023-08-23T10:07:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=5383"},"modified":"2023-08-29T16:48:08","modified_gmt":"2023-08-29T09:48:08","slug":"2-nguyen-nhan-met-moi-sau-khi-tap-luyen-tai-sao-va-cach-de-khac-phuc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/2-nguyen-nhan-met-moi-sau-khi-tap-luyen-tai-sao-va-cach-de-khac-phuc\/","title":{"rendered":"2 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n &#8211; T\u1ea1i sao v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><em><strong>2 Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n &#8211; t\u1ea1i sao v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The New Gym xem x\u00e9t l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c.<\/strong><\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, v\u00ec v\u1eady n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>The New Gym<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0xem x\u00e9t l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec g\u00e2y ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i v\u00e0o nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, h\u00e3y xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>C\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi ngay sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>M\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2;\"><strong>1. C\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi ngay sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi? C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, bao g\u1ed3m:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>M\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5587\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5587\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5587 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/mat-nuoc-2.png\" alt=\"m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/mat-nuoc-2.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/mat-nuoc-2-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/mat-nuoc-2-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/mat-nuoc-2-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/mat-nuoc-2-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5587\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 b\u00e0i ti\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n u\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trong v\u00e0 sau khi t\u1eadp (c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong ng\u00e0y). B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t qua vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>H\u1ea1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng huy\u1ebft<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5575\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5575\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5575 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ha-duong-huyet.png\" alt=\"m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ha-duong-huyet.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ha-duong-huyet-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ha-duong-huyet-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ha-duong-huyet-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ha-duong-huyet-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5575\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">H\u1ea1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng huy\u1ebft<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ebft glucose trong m\u00e1u v\u00e0 glucose \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 tr\u1eef trong c\u01a1 b\u1eafp (\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 glycogen). N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn cao, b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3ng glucose d\u1ef1 tr\u1eef c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, g\u00e2y ra h\u1ea1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng huy\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang n\u1ea1p n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0103n m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ch\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c b\u1eefa \u0103n nh\u1eb9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u carb v\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1ed9t \u00edt carb ngay sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung glycogen.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5579\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5579\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5579 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/cuong-do-tap-luyen.png\" alt=\"m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/cuong-do-tap-luyen.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/cuong-do-tap-luyen-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/cuong-do-tap-luyen-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/cuong-do-tap-luyen-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/cuong-do-tap-luyen-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5579\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">C\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 fan c\u1ee7a HIIT hay c\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng? M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t oxy v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra axit lactic, c\u1ea3 hai th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ti\u00eau hao n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u00edt oxy h\u01a1n (c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 glycogen), vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Gi\u1eef c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp HIIT trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ecdi b\u00e0i t\u1eadp HIIT nghe r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean t\u1eadp 1-2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2;\"><strong>2. M\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m sau ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y, th\u00ec c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1eadp qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5581\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5581\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5581 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ban-tap-qua-nhieu.png\" alt=\"m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ban-tap-qua-nhieu.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ban-tap-qua-nhieu-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ban-tap-qua-nhieu-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ban-tap-qua-nhieu-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ban-tap-qua-nhieu-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5581\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u1eadp qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111ang b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng? D\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m c\u01a1 v\u00e0 kh\u1edbp. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n, v\u00ec v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u2013 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n suy nh\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 ng\u00e0y\/tu\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngh\u1ec9 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 48 gi\u1edd gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u01a1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n \u0103n u\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4586\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4586\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4586 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/nhu-the-nao-la-che-do-dinh-duong-hop-ly-e1689817532328.png\" alt=\"m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/nhu-the-nao-la-che-do-dinh-duong-hop-ly-e1689817532328.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/nhu-the-nao-la-che-do-dinh-duong-hop-ly-e1689817532328-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/nhu-the-nao-la-che-do-dinh-duong-hop-ly-e1689817532328-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/nhu-the-nao-la-che-do-dinh-duong-hop-ly-e1689817532328-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/nhu-the-nao-la-che-do-dinh-duong-hop-ly-e1689817532328-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4586\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n \u0103n u\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf vi\u1ec7c \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7 calo, m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o n\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m ch\u1ea5t: Carb, Protein v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Carb gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, trong khi Protein r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u01a1 b\u1eafp. Ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 vitamin v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ba nh\u00f3m ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, do \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em><strong><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5583\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ngu-khong-du-giac.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ngu-khong-du-giac.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ngu-khong-du-giac-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ngu-khong-du-giac-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ngu-khong-du-giac-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ngu-khong-du-giac-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ngon gi\u1ea5c th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa khi b\u1ea1n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c cho ph\u00e9p c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. Khi b\u1ecb thi\u1ebfu ng\u1ee7, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb 6-8 ti\u1ebfng. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o nh\u1ecf sau \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon: kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 1 ti\u1ebfng, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eafm n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m, \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch ho\u1eb7c ng\u1ed3i thi\u1ec1n, t\u1eaft \u0111\u00e8n ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n b\u1ecb c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5589\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5589\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5589 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/bi-cang-thang-1.png\" alt=\"m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1040\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/bi-cang-thang-1.png 2048w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/bi-cang-thang-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/bi-cang-thang-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/bi-cang-thang-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/bi-cang-thang-1-1536x780.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5589\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n b\u1ecb c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta th\u1ec9nh tho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo l\u1eafng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>C\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c:<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0: ng\u1ed3i thi\u1ec1n, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/sau-tap-an-gi\/\">Sau t\u1eadp \u0103n g\u00ec? N\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o sau t\u1eadp?<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 